Title: Return to Hell
Writer: Joe Gayton (creator), Tony Gayton (creator), Jami O'Brien, Tom Brady (story editor), Michael C. Martin (staff writer), Jimmy Mero (staff writer)
Actors: Anson Mount, Colm Meaney, Christopher Heyerdahl, Robin McLeavy
Plot: Cullen, Durant and Campbell come together in order to discuss a means by which to provide protection to the citizens of Cheyenne. They must return a sense of well-being to the town after a disturbing act of violence takes place.
